cardiovascular_risk_score.formula: Sum of cardiovascular conditions (active=2, remote=1, absent=0)
cardiovascular_risk_score.rationale: CV disease is a major dementia risk factor
cardiovascular_risk_score.expected_impact: Higher score indicates higher dementia risk

cerebrovascular_risk_score.formula: Weighted sum: stroke (3 active, 2 remote) + multiple strokes (2) + TIA (2 active, 1 remote) + multiple TIA (1)
cerebrovascular_risk_score.rationale: Stroke and TIA strongly increase dementia risk
cerebrovascular_risk_score.expected_impact: Higher score indicates higher dementia risk

lifestyle_risk_score.formula: Current smoking (2) + ever smoked 100+ cigarettes (1) + alcohol abuse (2 active, 1 remote) + other substance abuse (2 active, 1 remote)
lifestyle_risk_score.rationale: Smoking and substance abuse increase dementia risk
lifestyle_risk_score.expected_impact: Higher score indicates higher dementia risk

functional_impairment_score.formula: Sum of difficulties across 10 activities: Normal=0, Difficulty=1, Assistance=2, Dependent=3
functional_impairment_score.rationale: Functional decline is early indicator of cognitive impairment
functional_impairment_score.expected_impact: Higher score indicates higher dementia risk

functional_domains_impaired.formula: Count of functional domains with any impairment (score >= 1)
functional_domains_impaired.rationale: Number of impaired domains indicates breadth of decline
functional_domains_impaired.expected_impact: More impaired domains indicates higher dementia risk

age_squared.rationale: Dementia risk increases exponentially with age

age_bins.rationale: Risk increases sharply at certain age thresholds

low_education.rationale: Low education is established dementia risk factor (cognitive reserve)

lives_alone.rationale: Social isolation is dementia risk factor
lives_alone.expected_impact: Living alone may increase dementia risk

pack_years.rationale: Pack-years is standard measure of smoking exposure

years_since_quit.formula: Current age - age when quit smoking
years_since_quit.rationale: Time since quitting affects risk reduction
years_since_quit.expected_impact: More years since quitting reduces risk

total_comorbidities.formula: Count of all medical conditions (active or remote)
total_comorbidities.rationale: Higher comorbidity burden increases dementia risk
total_comorbidities.expected_impact: More comorbidities indicates higher dementia risk

vision_impaired.formula: Vision problems even with corrective lenses
vision_impaired.rationale: Sensory impairment linked to cognitive decline
vision_impaired.expected_impact: Vision impairment may increase dementia risk

encoding.strategy: Label Encoding for low cardinality, One-Hot for medium cardinality

scaling.justification: RobustScaler is resilient to outliers, suitable for medical data
